-----------------------
- Software to Install -
-----------------------

1. Visual Studio Code: https://code.visualstudio.com/
2. Python: https://www.python.org/
3. Pygame: Instructions below

---------------------
- Installing Pygame -
---------------------

1. Click Windows or Start and type CMD
2. Open up the Command Prompt app
3. Make sure Python is already installed.
4. Type into the Command Prompt: pip install pygame
5. Hit enter.
6. Once it says it is successfully installed, exit out of the Command Prompt

